flowchart LR
    A[Unhandled production exception] --> B[ApplicationController#handle_error]
    B --> C[log_exception_details]
    C --> D[BetterTogether report_error]
    D --> E[AdapterRegistry.dispatch :error_reporting]
    E --> F[Reporter adapter 1]
    E --> G[Reporter adapter 2]
    E --> H[Reporter adapter N]
    F --> I{failure?}
    I -- yes --> J[log AdapterDispatchFailure]
    I -- no --> K[adapter success]
    G --> L{failure?}
    L -- yes --> J
    L -- no --> K
    H --> M{failure?}
    M -- yes --> J
    M -- no --> K
    J --> N[raise DispatchError after fan-out completes]
    N --> O[ApplicationController logs ErrorReportingFailure]
    K --> P[500 response still rendered to user]
    O --> P
